I donated, did you? Link in bio. Our brother and highly influential contributor to the punk rock culture, Chris Flippin needs our help and support!!! . 

As many of you already know, our dear friend Chris Flippin is facing a severe health crisis after experiencing a cardiac emergency in Germany while on tour with Versus The World. He is currently dealing with various life altering heart conditions. He now requires ongoing medical attention, including a myriad of medications, heart rhythm reset, doctor visits, follow ups, procedures, physical therapy, and whatever else is needed. His situation is exacerbated by the fact that he is unable to work or tour. Strenuous activities and physical labor are strictly prohibited for his safety during his recovery period. Which is currently undetermined until his condition improves.

It is well known that the health care system in the U.S. is inequitable and overpriced. And the cost of living continues to rise. We’re rallying to raise funds for Chris’s medical needs, living expenses, and to show some gratitude for his contributions as a musician. Please give what you can to aid his recovery and support him during this challenging time. Your donations, help, and support are greatly appreciated.
